  "notes": "Isfahani Persian (Eṣfahānī). Isfahan — former Safavid capital. Similar to Tehran but: /æ/ → [ɛ] before nasals; uvular [ɢ] somewhat more frequent; slightly less vowel reduction of unstressed syllables. Historically considered a prestige variety alongside Tehran.",
